summary: A really, really overpowered companion. Not to mention he looks like me. :)
descriptionHtml:
An extremely overpowered companion located just outside of Solitude. I made this mod because I wanted a companion that looks like me and to test out the Creation Kit. This is my first mod, so comments are extremely appreciated!

Stats:
Name: Damon Cole
Race: Breton
Level: 130
Spells: ALL of the Master-level spells in every school.
Location: Just outside of Solitude.
Skill level: 105 in everything.
author: TheJediCreed
